on rightclick with gold ingot:
    if uncolored name of event-item is "[ 샤크스마스 ] 코인 10개 압축" or "[ 샤크스마스 ] 코인 ⚝":
        set {randombox.christmas::%uuid of player%} to 0 if {randombox.christmas::%uuid of player%} isn't set
        set {_i} to {randombox.christmas::%uuid of player%}
        if item amount of player's tool < 2:
            send "{@prefix} 코인 2개를 손에 들고 우클릭해주세요."
            stop
        remove 2 of player's tool from player's tool
        set {_n} to random integer between 1 and 200
